
The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind ni filime yikinamico yo mu Bwongereza yo mu 2019 yanditswe, iyoborwa na Chiwetel Ejiofor . Filime ishingiye kuri memoire y'izina  na William Kamkwamba na Bryan Mealer. Yerekanwe mu gice cya Premieres mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 kandi itangira kunyura kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019. Yatoranijwe  muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga Yamamaye mu bihembo bya 92 bya Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe. 

