== Kurekurwa ==
Ku ya 14 Ugushyingo 2018, Netflix yabonye uburenganzira bwo gukwirakwiza ku isi, usibye Ubuyapani, Ubushinwa, n'Ubwongereza.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 ku ya 25 Mutarama 2019.  Nyuma yaje gusohoka kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019.
